- Began structured endurance running approximately [X] years ago.
- Training methodology: [e.g., Jack Daniels VDOT / Pfitzinger / self-coached]
- Comfortable with: Easy (E), Marathon (M), Threshold (T), Interval (I), Repetition (R) pacing zones.

